Kan Någon SEEDA ! ?
Fast Som Övriga På 99,9

Guys, I stucked also in 99,9% but managed to burn a 100% dvdr with two "guides" ,
Swedish; Ni som sitter fast på 99,9%...stoppa nerladningen öppna mappen och kasta bort t.ex. Nfo-filen och SFV-filen starta nerladningen igen Detta brukar funka för mej..
English; For those who got stucked on 99,9% just stop the download, delete for example the .nfo file or .SFV file and start the download again. This usually works for me!

And after you've got 91 perfect rar-files (part 011, 051 and 092 are not complete, only 46,6 mb each), just try this; Right-click the rar-file part001, choose extract files..., "Extraction path and options" -window opens, check the box "Keep broken files". Then save settings and press "OK". Works with me, you guys try it too.
cheers :D
